                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970215-2-defend54 t17970215-2-punish10"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 32.)</p>
               <p>Mackaway, Guilty Death. (Aged 25.)</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron THOMPSON.</p>
